{"id":280220,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【图说天朝】希望小学成了垃圾场/","date":"2013-02-21T09:38:37Z","modified":"2013-02-21T09:38:37Z","title":"【图说天朝】希望小学成了垃圾场","content":"<p>2月19日，贵州省凯里市龙场镇老山村。一处建成仅4年的希望小学便遭废弃，变成了一个垃圾回收站。这所小学位于位于半山腰，前后都是数百米的悬崖。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-F8Wt49mIJBI/USV95L-YgKI/AAAAAAAAnlQ/YeC_fa_3IA8/s1095/BEE8E973FA38011BFE55E2DC5BF22A41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-s422TM3Qyew/USV-pLvS1eI/AAAAAAAAnlY/Gy1i-p9TLxc/s1095/8O64J3PA00AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" /></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,21627,13770],"tags":[22334,22333]}